---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout title="About — Ivaylo Kolev" description="About Ivaylo Kolev — who I am, what I build, and where I'm headed." activeNav="about">

  <style is:global>
    .about-layout{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 340px;gap:4rem;padding:5rem 3rem;position:relative;z-index:1;align-items:start;}
    .about-section{margin-bottom:3rem;}
    .about-section-label{font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:0.68rem;color:var(--gold);letter-spacing:0.25em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:0.75rem;padding-bottom:0.75rem;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);}
    .about-section p{font-size:0.95rem;color:var(--text-mid);line-height:1.85;margin-bottom:1rem;}
    .about-section p:last-child{margin-bottom:0;}
    .about-section strong{color:var(--text);font-weight:500;}
    .about-sidebar{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1.25rem;}
    .sidebar-card{background:var(--bg-card);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:3px;padding:1.4rem;}
    .sidebar-card-label{font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:0.6rem;letter-spacing:0.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold);margin-bottom:1rem;}
    .fact-item{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0.15rem;padding:0.6rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);}
    .fact-item:last-child{border-bottom:none;padding-bottom:0;}
    .fact-label{font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:0.6rem;color:var(--text-muted);letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;}
    .fact-value{font-size:0.85rem;color:var(--text-mid);}
    .sidebar-list{list-style:none;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0.5rem;}
    .sidebar-list li{font-size:0.84rem;color:var(--text-mid);display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:0.5rem;}
    .sidebar-list li::before{content:'—';color:var(--text-muted);font-size:0.7rem;flex-shrink:0;}
    .sidebar-list li strong{color:var(--text);font-weight:500;}
    .sidebar-geo{display:flex;justify-content:center;padding:1rem 0;opacity:0.1;}
    .timeline{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0;}
    .timeline-item{display:grid;grid-template-columns:72px 1fr;gap:1.5rem;position:relative;padding-bottom:2rem;}
    .timeline-item::before{content:'';position:absolute;left:calc(72px + 0.75rem - 0.5px);top:20px;bottom:0;width:1px;background:var(--border);}
    .timeline-item:last-child::before{display:none;}
    .timeline-year{font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:0.68rem;color:var(--gold);letter-spacing:0.1em;padding-top:2px;}
    .timeline-dot{width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--gold);border:2px solid var(--bg);position:absolute;left:calc(72px + 0.75rem - 4px);top:3px;}
    .timeline-title{font-size:0.92rem;font-weight:500;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:0.25rem;}
    .timeline-desc{font-size:0.82rem;color:var(--text-muted);line-height:1.6;}
    @media(max-width:1000px){.about-layout{grid-template-columns:1fr;}}
    @media(max-width:768px){.about-layout{padding-left:1.5rem;padding-right:1.5rem;}}
  </style>

  <div class="page-header">
    <p class="page-eyebrow">// The longer version</p>
    <h1 class="page-title">About Me</h1>
    <p class="page-sub">I'm Ivaylo — builder, automator, and storyteller. I go by I2KGhost online. Here's the full story.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="divider"></div>

  <div class="about-layout">

    <div class="about-main">

      <div class="about-section reveal">
        <p class="about-section-label">// Who I am</p>
        <p>I'm Ivaylo Kolev — a Bulgarian-born builder based in London. Online I go by <strong>I2KGhost</strong>. The name started as a shortened version of my own name, with Ghost added because I've always been drawn to shadows, hidden things, and anything slightly mysterious.</p>
        <p>By day I work at Amazon. Outside of work I build tools, chase AI and security certifications, and develop a fantasy universe called Drekoria that's been living in my head since I was a teenager.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="about-section reveal">
        <p class="about-section-label">// How I got into tech</p>
        <p>My first serious encounter with code was around 2007–2008 at a computer networks college. I had no idea what was happening. It wasn't until years later — when a private university in Bulgaria opened free programming courses — that I actually got hooked. Java first, then C, C++, C#, and eventually Python.</p>
        <p>Python stuck. I can read, write, and debug my way through real problems. That's been enough to build things that actually work.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="about-section reveal">
        <p class="about-section-label">// What I'm building now</p>
        <p>My main focus right now is <strong>Croft Guide</strong> — a free tool that helps small UK farmers understand which government grants and subsidies they qualify for. Built ahead of the SFI 2026 rollout, when 64% of small farmers say they're confused by the new schemes.</p>
        <p>In parallel I'm working through the <strong>AWS AI & ML Scholars program</strong> — a free global program by AWS and Udacity — and the <strong>TryHackMe AI Security path</strong>, because building with AI and understanding how it can be exploited are increasingly the same skill set.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="about-section reveal">
        <p class="about-section-label">// The path behind me</p>
        <div class="timeline">
          <div class="timeline-item">
            <span class="timeline-year">2007</span>
            <div class="timeline-content">
              <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
              <p class="timeline-title">First encounter with code</p>
              <p class="timeline-desc">Computer networks college in Bulgaria. No idea what was happening, but something stuck.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-item">
            <span class="timeline-year">2012</span>
            <div class="timeline-content">
              <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
              <p class="timeline-title">Got hooked on programming</p>
              <p class="timeline-desc">Free university courses — Java, C++, C#, Python. Python eventually became the one that stuck.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-item">
            <span class="timeline-year">2015</span>
            <div class="timeline-content">
              <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
              <p class="timeline-title">Drekoria begins</p>
              <p class="timeline-desc">A fantasy novel idea. An empire named Drekoria. The book stalled — the world never stopped growing.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-item">
            <span class="timeline-year">2018</span>
            <div class="timeline-content">
              <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
              <p class="timeline-title">Moved to London</p>
              <p class="timeline-desc">Started in hospitality — Grange Hotels, then Leonardo Hotels. Began taking automation and AI seriously.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-item">
            <span class="timeline-year">2021</span>
            <div class="timeline-content">
              <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
              <p class="timeline-title">Joined Amazon</p>
              <p class="timeline-desc">Started at Amazon fulfillment. Became an Auditor within 3 months. AI and automation shifted from hobby to direction.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-item">
            <span class="timeline-year">2026</span>
            <div class="timeline-content">
              <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
              <p class="timeline-title">Building in public</p>
              <p class="timeline-desc">Croft Guide, AWS Scholars, AI security — and finally a home for all of it at ivaylokolev.net.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="about-sidebar">

      <div class="sidebar-card reveal">
        <p class="sidebar-card-label">Quick facts</p>
        <div>
          <div class="fact-item"><span class="fact-label">Based in</span><span class="fact-value">London, UK</span></div>
          <div class="fact-item"><span class="fact-label">Originally from</span><span class="fact-value">Bulgaria</span></div>
          <div class="fact-item"><span class="fact-label">Online alias</span><span class="fact-value">I2KGhost</span></div>
          <div class="fact-item"><span class="fact-label">Day job</span><span class="fact-value">Amazon</span></div>
          <div class="fact-item"><span class="fact-label">Keyboard</span><span class="fact-value">Keychron Q1 Max</span></div>
          <div class="fact-item"><span class="fact-label">Favourite drink</span><span class="fact-value">Red wine. Or lemonade.</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="sidebar-card reveal">
        <p class="sidebar-card-label">Tools I use</p>
        <ul class="sidebar-list">
          <li><strong>Python</strong> for scripting and automation</li>
          <li><strong>n8n / Make.com</strong> for workflows</li>
          <li><strong>Astro</strong> for this site</li>
          <li><strong>Claude, ChatGPT</strong> daily AI tools</li>
          <li><strong>Brave + ProtonMail</strong> privacy stack</li>
          <li><strong>Adobe Premiere Pro</strong> for video</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="sidebar-card reveal">
        <p class="sidebar-card-label">Currently learning</p>
        <ul class="sidebar-list">
          <li>AWS AI Practitioner — Skill Builder</li>
          <li>TryHackMe AI Security Path</li>
          <li>Anthropic Academy — prompt engineering</li>
          <li>SPIN Selling — Neil Rackham</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="sidebar-geo" aria-hidden="true">
        <svg width="120" height="120" viewBox="0 0 120 120" fill="none">
          <rect x="10" y="10" width="45" height="45" stroke="#c9923a" stroke-width="1"/>
          <rect x="65" y="10" width="45" height="45" stroke="#c9923a" stroke-width="1"/>
          <rect x="10" y="65" width="45" height="45" stroke="#c9923a" stroke-width="1"/>
          <rect x="65" y="65" width="45" height="45" stroke="#c9923a" stroke-width="1"/>
          <rect x="22" y="22" width="21" height="21" stroke="#3ecfbe" stroke-width="0.5"/>
          <rect x="77" y="77" width="21" height="21" stroke="#3ecfbe" stroke-width="0.5"/>
          <line x1="55" y1="32" x2="65" y2="32" stroke="#c9923a" stroke-width="0.5" stroke-dasharray="2 4"/>
          <line x1="60" y1="55" x2="60" y2="65" stroke="#c9923a" stroke-width="0.5" stroke-dasharray="2 4"/>
        </svg>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

</PageLayout>
